# ARBITRAGE-PRO Execution Diagrams

## Execution Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Click Execute] --> B{Authentication Valid?}
    
    B -->|No| C[Redirect to Login]
    B -->|Yes| D{Opportunity Expired?}
    
    D -->|Yes| E[Show Error]
    D -->|No| F{Risk Tier?}
    
    F -->|Manual| G[Create Dry Run]
    F -->|Simulated| H[Run Simulation]
    F -->|Automated| I[Check Guardrails]
    
    I --> J{All Pass?}
    J -->|No| K[Log Block]
    J -->|Yes| L[Execute Buy Order]
    
    L --> M{Buy Filled?}
    M -->|No| N[Retry/Cancel]
    M -->|Yes| O[Execute Sell Order]
    
    O --> P{Sell Filled?}
    P -->|No| Q[Retry/Cancel]
    P -->|Yes| R[Calculate P&L]
    
    R --> S[Record Trade]
    S --> T[Update Stats]
    T --> U[Send Notification]
    
    G --> V[Show Review UI]
    H --> W[Show Results]
    K --> X[Show Block Reason]
    N --> Y[Show Error]
    Q --> Y
    
    V --> Z[Await User Action]
    Z --> AA{User Approves?}
    AA -->|Yes| L
    AA -->|No| AB[Discard]
```

