## Manual Execution Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI
    participant API
    participant DB
    participant Exchange
    
    User->>UI: View Opportunity
    UI->>API: GET /opportunities/:id
    API->>DB: Fetch Opportunity
    DB-->>API: Opportunity Data
    API-->>UI: Opportunity Details
    
    User->>UI: Click Execute
    UI->>API: POST /execute
    API->>DB: Create Dry Run
    DB-->>API: Trade ID
    API-->>UI: Dry Run Created
    
    UI->>User: Show Review Screen
    Note over UI: Display: Buy Price, Sell Price, Fees, Expected Profit
    
    User->>UI: Confirm Trade
    UI->>API: POST /confirm
    API->>Exchange: Place Buy Order
    Exchange-->>API: Order Filled
    API->>Exchange: Place Sell Order
    Exchange-->>API: Order Filled
    
    API->>DB: Record Trade
    DB-->>API: Trade Saved
    API-->>UI: Success
    
    UI->>User: Show Results
```

## Automated Execution Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Worker
    participant API
    participant Guardrails
    participant Safety
    participant Exchange
    participant DB
    
    Worker->>API: Execute Opportunity
    API->>DB: Get Opportunity
    DB-->>API: Opportunity Data
    
    API->>Guardrails: Check All Guardrails
    Guardrails-->>API: Result
    
    alt Guardrails Pass
        API->>Safety: Safety Check
        Safety-->>API: Approved
        
        API->>Exchange: Place Buy Order (Market)
        Exchange-->>API: Buy Filled @ Price
        
        API->>Exchange: Place Sell Order (Market)
        Exchange-->>API: Sell Filled @ Price
        
        API->>API: Calculate P&L
        
        API->>DB: Record Trade
        DB-->>API: Trade ID
        
        API->>DB: Update Stats
        API->>Worker: Notify Complete
        
        Worker->>Worker: Log Success
    else Guardrails Fail
        API->>DB: Log Block Reason
        API-->>Worker: Blocked
        
        Worker->>Worker: Log Failure
    end
```

