## Circuit Breaker State Machine

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CLOSED
    
    CLOSED --> OPEN: Failure Count >= 3
    OPEN --> HALF_OPEN: After 5 minutes
    HALF_OPEN --> CLOSED: Success
    HALF_OPEN --> OPEN: Failure
    
    OPEN --> OPEN: Requests Rejected
    
    note right of CLOSED
        Normal operation
        All requests allowed
    end note
    
    note right of OPEN
        Circuit tripped
        All requests blocked
        Alert ops team
    end note
    
    note right of HALF_OPEN
        Testing recovery
        Limited requests
    end note
```

## Retry Logic

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Attempt 1] --> B{Success?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Return Result]
    B -->|No| D{Retries Left?}
    
    D -->|No| E[Throw Error]
    D -->|Yes| F[Wait 1s + Jitter]
    
    F --> G[Attempt 2]
    G --> H{Success?}
    H -->|Yes| C
    H -->|No| I{Retries Left?}
    
    I -->|No| E
    I -->|Yes| J[Wait 2s + Jitter]
    
    J --> K[Attempt 3]
    K --> L{Success?}
    L -->|Yes| C
    L -->|No| E
    
    E --> M[Circuit Breaker]
    M --> N[Open Circuit]
```

## Kill Switch Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Trigger Event] --> B{Event Type?}
    
    B -->|Daily Loss| C[Pause 24h]
    B -->|API Errors| D[Pause 5min]
    B -->|Manual| E[Pause 24h]
    B -->|Circuit Breaker| F[Pause 5min]
    
    C --> G[Set Auto-Paused Until]
    D --> G
    E --> G
    F --> G
    
    G --> H[Cancel All Pending]
    H --> I[Alert User]
    I --> J[Log Event]
    
    J --> K[Notify Ops]
    
    L[User Resume] --> M{Cooldown OK?}
    M -->|No| N[Deny Resume]
    M -->|Yes| O[Clear Pause]
    
    O --> P[Resume Trading]
```

## Trade Lifecycle

```mermaid
flowchart TD
