## Error Recovery

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Error Detected] --> B{Error Type?}
    
    B -->|Network| C[Retry with Backoff]
    B -->|Rate Limit| D[Wait + Retry]
    B -->|Insufficient Balance| E[Skip Trade]
    B -->|Invalid Price| F[Cancel Orders]
    B -->|Timeout| G[Check Status]
    
    C --> H{Retry Exhausted?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Circuit Breaker]
    H -->|No| J[Resume]
    
    D --> K{Honor Retry-After?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Wait]
    K -->|No| M[Backoff]
    
    L --> N[Retry]
    M --> N
    
    E --> O[Log + Alert]
    F --> O
    G --> P{Status?}
    P -->|Pending| Q[Wait More]
    P -->|Failed| R[Cancel All]
    P -->|Success| S[Continue]
    
    I --> T[Alert Ops]
    O --> T
    R --> T
    
    T --> U[Kill Switch?]
    U -->|Yes| V[Pause All]
    U -->|No| W[Continue]